1998-2003 Ford PowerStroke 7.3L and Navistar T444E High Pressure Oil Pump Reservoir Gasket

This Oil Reservoir Gasket offers a cost-savings advantage when servicing part of the vehicles timing cover. Our Oil Reservoir Gasket is now available as a separate component, enabling you to replace only the failed original gasket, instead of the entire timing cover assembly, saving time, money and labor.
